      "source": [
        "## 🔧 Step 6 — Preprocessing Pipeline (ColumnTransformer)\n",
        "\n",
        "> Uses `sklearn.Pipeline` internally, so **no data leakage** occurs between train and test sets."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
